    dc:creator "Meegaskumbura, Madhava; Manamendra-Arachchi, Kelum; Schneider, Christopher J.; Pethiyagoda, And Rohan" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "New species amongst Sri Lanka’s extinct shrub frogs (Amphibia: Rhacophoridae: Philautus)" ;
